title: Welcome
text:
I’m a digital marketing student passionate about blending creativity with data to build brands, drive engagement, and solve real-world business problems.
Currently studying at Cal Poly Pomona, I’m developing skills in:
- Social media strategy & content creation
- Data analytics using R & Excel
- Email marketing, SEO, and campaign management
I’m actively seeking opportunities to apply my knowledge in digital marketing, brand development, and marketing analytics. If you’re looking for someone with a mix of analytical insight and creative energy—I’d love to connect.
